abstract: >-
  A structured, machine-readable database of 282+ privacy and data protection
  skills for AI agents following the agentskills.io open standard. Covers GDPR,
  CCPA/CPRA, LGPD, PIPL, India DPDP Act, HIPAA, EU AI Act, and 10+ additional
  jurisdictions across 20 compliance domains. Each skill includes YAML frontmatter
  for relevance matching, step-by-step workflows, regulatory citations with
  enforcement precedents, Python automation scripts, and filled real-world
  templates. Compatible with Claude Code, GitHub Copilot, OpenAI Codex CLI,
  Cursor, Gemini CLI, and 26+ AI platforms.
